snippet.title: Star Iliad - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!
✨ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1649670/

From the developers of "Phoenotopia" comes "Star Iliad"!

Step into the boots of Blythe Braves, a daring Star Ranger stranded inside the mythical Star Whale—a gargantuan, living cosmic entity. Venture deep into the whale’s mysterious organs, a world brimming with wonder, danger, and unforgettable characters.

Currently in development! Follow the journey via the link below:
💫https://stariliad.com/
